{"tid":1069577,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大麻咖啡店 政府管唔掂","createTime":"2019-03-20T05:21:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-20T18:12:08.000Z","uid":130626,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c8e77788d1a9301ccbbaf97a54533eef13daf619","tid":1069577,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T05:21:05.000Z","msg":"中學生疑接收大麻花郵包，醫院醫生涉當值期間「隊草」，近日涉及大麻案件急升。本報發現有海外網店可郵寄大麻產品予本港買家，港島區鬧市更有樓上舖變身「大麻咖啡店」，有顧客公然在食肆內吸食大麻，但無人過問。附近商戶怒轟長期受大麻氣味滋擾，擔心「毒竇」或招惹不法分子聚集，影響治安。立法會議員指外國大麻合法化令其潛在禍害受忽視，促港府加強巡查及宣傳教育。<br />\n「特別係星期五、六，陣味勁到走廊都聞到！」陳先生（化名）的商舖鄰近「大麻咖啡店」，近一年來，一直飽受咖啡店傳出的大麻氣味困擾。「試過上門理論，但咖啡店負責人竟然話，啲客要食，佢都冇計！」陳又指，不時有咖啡店的顧客疑似受酒精或藥物影響後暈倒在樓梯間，嘔吐物散落一地，咖啡店卻未有派人清理。<br />\n<img src=\"https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20190318/photo/0318-00174-001b1.jpg?t=1553059129796\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190318%2Fphoto%2F0318-00174-001b1.jpg%3Ft%3D1553059129796&h=f5eff465&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n咖啡店整晚瀰漫着濃烈的大麻和煙草氣味，附近商戶怒轟長期受氣味滋擾。<br />\n<img src=\"https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20190318/photo/0318-00174-001b2.jpg?t=1553059137646\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190318%2Fphoto%2F0318-00174-001b2.jpg%3Ft%3D1553059137646&h=02a8319a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有外籍青年等候「上電」期間，將整包大麻花（箭嘴示）直接放在餐桌上。<br />\n<img src=\"https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20190318/photo/0318-00174-001b3.jpg?t=1553059146258\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190318%2Fphoto%2F0318-00174-001b3.jpg%3Ft%3D1553059146258&h=69114a85&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不少濫用大麻的人會將大麻混合煙草吸食。<br />\n<img src=\"https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20190318/photo/0318-00174-001b4.jpg?t=1553059155106\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190318%2Fphoto%2F0318-00174-001b4.jpg%3Ft%3D1553059155106&h=0be0ed1c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n位於駱克道的涉事咖啡店設有露台。<br />\n<img src=\"https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20190318/photo/0318-00174-001b5.jpg?t=1553059165346\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190318%2Fphoto%2F0318-00174-001b5.jpg%3Ft%3D1553059165346&h=bc028813&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「大麻咖啡店」內有不少外籍人士，有知情者指當中不少為大學交流生。<br />\n<img src=\"https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20190318/photo/0318-00174-001b6.jpg?t=1553059174602\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190318%2Fphoto%2F0318-00174-001b6.jpg%3Ft%3D1553059174602&h=a4ee8a35&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n市民反應<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=o52HcF_gSYA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Do52HcF_gSYA&d=0gDP8yh%2BwNUcUrQXLcOs9BX1SmvCJyfLMOcbfj5ioUM%3D&h=842178c1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=o52HcF_gSYA</a>"},{"pid":"02da30ce78e7598b13cd20b5091fff09167fa4b4","tid":1069577,"uid":8441,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T05:48:13.000Z","msg":"咩名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d522000e87b1de454aaadbd6680d3f1509678ef","tid":1069577,"uid":56902,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T05:49:59.000Z","msg":"間接宣傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0cfb956ba8bcf1905f2b6d76a7c2f51b010f81e","tid":1069577,"uid":95,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T06:19:14.000Z","msg":"做乜貼舊聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"604bc682e2eefde229e8c12589e7dbedd85e0a70","tid":1069577,"uid":20658,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T06:43:08.000Z","msg":"班死道友準備全面進場"},{"pid":"d8d691299dee3bb93cf50b7fa72bf12355fed796","tid":1069577,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e0cfb956ba8bcf1905f2b6d76a7c2f51b010f81e","tid":1069577,"uid":95,"li